menuconfig MODULES_TRACKING
	bool "tracking"
	default n
	---help---
		TRACKING mode — visual-servo from external seeker errors.
		Receives TRACKING_MESSAGE (MAVLink ID 11045) and runs roll/pitch/throttle
		PIDs, publishing vehicle_attitude_setpoint when in NAVIGATION_STATE_EXTERNAL1.
		Vehicle-type-aware: fixed-wing uses thrust_body[0] with pitch-for-airspeed
		throttle; multicopter uses thrust_body[2] with altitude-hold throttle vs
		TRK_TGT_ALT.
